query:
-- Create Bracelets category
INSERT INTO categories (name, slug, description, displayOrder) VALUES ('Bracelets', 'bracelets', 'Handmade beaded bracelets featuring natural stones and resin', 3);

-- Add Map Jasper Bracelet
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, price, categoryId, images, materials, stockQuantity, isAvailable) 
SELECT 
  'Map Jasper Bracelet',
  'map-jasper-bracelet',
  'Elegant bracelet featuring 6mm map jasper natural stone beads with distinctive gray marbled patterns, accented with silver spacer beads. Perfect for everyday wear.',
  10.00,
  id,
  JSON_ARRAY(
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/jPgPNxRizxrpPrqw.png', 'alt', 'Map Jasper Bracelet'),
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/lFOJWqkKCadRihuQ.png', 'alt', 'Map Jasper Bracelet Size Reference')
  ),
  JSON_ARRAY('6mm Map Jasper Beads', 'Silver Spacer Beads'),
  10,
  1
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'bracelets';

-- Add Lava Stone Bracelet
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, price, categoryId, images, materials, stockQuantity, isAvailable) 
SELECT 
  'Lava Stone Flower Bracelet',
  'lava-stone-flower-bracelet',
  'Striking bracelet featuring 6mm black lava stone beads with unique porous texture, beautifully accented with 6-petal alloy flower spacer beads in red and gold tones. Lava stone is known for its grounding properties.',
  10.00,
  id,
  JSON_ARRAY(
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/bjxLDPVwpseVtZOc.png', 'alt', 'Lava Stone Flower Bracelet'),
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/eUDYAIuNGxtfVOmQ.png', 'alt', 'Lava Stone Flower Bracelet Size Reference')
  ),
  JSON_ARRAY('6mm Lava Stone Beads', '6-Petal Alloy Flower Spacer Beads'),
  10,
  1
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'bracelets';

-- Add Starry Sky Resin Bracelet
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, price, categoryId, images, materials, stockQuantity, isAvailable) 
SELECT 
  'Starry Sky Resin Bracelet',
  'starry-sky-resin-bracelet',
  'Magical bracelet featuring colorful starry sky resin beads filled with glitter that sparkles like a galaxy, accented with a silver spacer bead. Each bead is unique with its own color gradient and sparkle pattern.',
  9.00,
  id,
  JSON_ARRAY(
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/CQdiCmHQGgFBdxZs.png', 'alt', 'Starry Sky Resin Bracelet'),
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/QgRzxeASLEwLNfyx.png', 'alt', 'Starry Sky Resin Bracelet Size Reference')
  ),
  JSON_ARRAY('Starry Sky Resin Beads with Glitter', 'Silver Spacer Bead'),
  10,
  1
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'bracelets';

-- Add Super Seven Crystal Bracelet
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, price, categoryId, images, materials, stockQuantity, isAvailable) 
SELECT 
  'Black Golden Super Seven Crystal Bracelet',
  'black-golden-super-seven-crystal-bracelet',
  'Premium bracelet featuring 8mm black golden super seven crystal beads with stunning golden and copper rutile inclusions. Super seven is a rare combination of seven minerals and is highly valued for its metaphysical properties.',
  16.00,
  id,
  JSON_ARRAY(
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/hejQXuJulPnQSuzc.png', 'alt', 'Black Golden Super Seven Crystal Bracelet'),
    JSON_OBJECT('url', 'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/zBmfpONMBZpEyAWq.png', 'alt', 'Black Golden Super Seven Crystal Bracelet Size Reference')
  ),
  JSON_ARRAY('8mm Black Golden Super Seven Crystal Beads'),
  10,
  1
FROM categories WHERE slug = 'bracelets';
